  ],
  "remarks": "Polyus Research Institute is a Russian military industry company. It produces laser technological installations, semiconductor and solid-state lasers, laser rangefinders and target designators dedicated for high precision weapons. Products of Polyus Research Institute can be found in, for example, Sosna-1 missiles and 2S9 “Nona” self-propelled mortar that are used by the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. Moreover, the company supplies weapons to the Ministry of Defence of the Russian Federation under Russia’s state defence order.",
